<div class="card mt-5" style="background-color:antiquewhite">
    <div class="card-header">
        <img src="https://www.admissionindia.net/uploads/colleges/31/logo-1.png" style="height:70px" />
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">




        <div class="responsive-container-block bigContainer">
            <div class="responsive-container-block Container">
                <div class="imgContainer">
                    <img class="blueDots" src="https://workik-widget-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/widget-assets/images/aw3.svg">
                    <img class="mainImg" src="https://workik-widget-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/widget-assets/images/aw2.svg">
                </div>
                <div class="responsive-container-block textSide">
                    <p class="text-blk heading">
                        About Us
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-blk subHeading">
                        Established in 1994 by Shri Jai Narain Chouksey, the LNCT Group, part of the H. K. Kalchuri Educational Trust, epitomizes educational excellence. Committed to nurturing skilled professionals, the group offers leading programs in engineering, management, pharmacy, and medical fields. With ISO-9001 certification and NBA accreditation for various engineering courses, LNCT Group is a preferred choice for bright minds nationwide. Its sprawling 50-acre campus in Bhopal boasts modern amenities including Wi-Fi, digital library, and sports facilities, fostering a conducive environment for learning and growth. With alumni spread across the globe, LNCT Group remains at the forefront of producing industry-ready talent.
                    </p>
                    <div class="responsive-cell-block wk-desk-6 wk-ipadp-6 wk-tab-12 wk-mobile-12">
                        <div class="cardImgContainer">
                            <img class="cardImg" src="https://lnct.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Jai-Narain-Chouksey.png">
                        </div>
                        <div class="cardText">
                            <p class="text-blk cardHeading">
                                Shri Jai Narayan Chouksey
                                "Chairman"
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-blk cardSubHeading">
                                Education is what remains after one has forgotten what one has learned in school”. At LNCT University, the purpose of life is taught. The technology persists for products but the thought technologies in school are introduced to prepare the scholar for understanding the Education for life.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="responsive-cell-block wk-desk-6 wk-ipadp-6 wk-tab-12 wk-mobile-12">
                        <div class="cardImgContainer">
                            <img class="cardImg" src="https://lnct.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Poonam-Chouksey-.png">
                        </div>
                        <div class="cardText">
                            <p class="text-blk cardHeading">
                                Smt. Poonam Chouksey
                                "Vice Chairperson"
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-blk cardSubHeading">
                                I welcome you to this campus of higher learning which is being the prime unit of LNCT Group of Colleges.In my view,your decision to choose lnct is right and wise.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="responsive-cell-block wk-desk-6 wk-ipadp-6 wk-tab-12 wk-mobile-12">
                        <div class="cardImgContainer">
                            <img class="cardImg" src="https://lnct.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Anupam-Chouksey.png">
                        </div>
                        <div class="cardText">
                            <p class="text-blk cardHeading">
                                Dr. Anupam Chouksey
                                "Secretary"
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-blk cardSubHeading">
                                I believe learning is the only tool for success of an individual irrespective of age.At LNCT,we are committed for betterment of society through development of individuals of students in every stage.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">
                        <button  class="explore">
                            Explore our Services
                        </button>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <img class="redDots" src="https://workik-widget-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/widget-assets/images/cw3.svg">
            </div>
        </div>







    </div>
</div>











